title: Windows 8.1 KMS Activator Ultimate v1.4
description:
Description:
Safe activator with no harm to System Files
Period of activation is 180 days and you can renew it
You can remove any previous activations
You can know informations about your activation,
your window s serial and the rest days of activation

It Activates :
Windows 8.1 Pro
Windows 8.1 Enterprise
Windows Server 2012 R2 Server Standard
Windows Server 2012 R2 Datacenter
Windows Server 2012 R2 Essentials

Add New features in v1.4
-New Design
-Stable Version
-Update KMS server every day
-Add Activation:
 Windows Server 2012 R2 Server Standard.
 Windows Server 2012 R2 Datacenter.
 Windows Server 2012 R2 Essentials.
-Fixed all bug.

Requirements:
Net Framework 2.0
Internet Connection

Installation:
1] Run As Administrator to work
2] Click Uninstall Product Key
3] Click "Update Server" to Update KMS Server
4] Click on which version of Windows you
5] Done, Enjoy :)

With Regards,
AmanPC
